{"bookId": "67656cf0a790fd9b172cf0d2", "moduleId": "67656cf0a790fd9b172cf0d2", "subjectId": "67656cf9a790fd9b172cf0df", "chapterId": "67656cf9a790fd9b172cf0e1", "subject": "Mathematics", "chapter": "Miscellaneous Mathematics", "count": 1, "questions": [{"id": 0, "subject": "Mathematics", "chapter": "Miscellaneous Mathematics", "exam": "Engineering", "examName": "Top 100 Numerical Qs of JEE Main 2023-2020", "q": "If <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>{</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>|</mo><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>}</mo><mo>,</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>:</mo><msqrt><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>,</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>{</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>|</mo><mo>&#10878;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>}</mo></math> and <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Z</mi></math> is the set of all integers, then the number of subsets of the set <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>C</mi><msup><mo>)</mo><mi>c</mi></msup><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>Z</mi></math> is _________.", "options": ["A", "B", "C", "D"], "answer": 0, "solution": "<blockquote><p>For First set&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>{</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>|</mo><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>}</mo></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo></math>&nbsp;Value which&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi></math>&nbsp;contains lies from&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>&#8746;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p>For second set&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced close=\"}\" open=\"{\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>:</mo><msqrt><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn></msqrt><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo></math>&nbsp;Value which&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>B</mi></math>&nbsp;contains lies from&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>&#8746;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p>For third set&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>{</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mi>R</mi><mo>:</mo><mo>|</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>|</mo><mo>&#10878;</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>}</mo></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo></math>&nbsp;Value which&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>C</mi></math>&nbsp;contains lies from&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8712;</mo><mo>(</mo><mo>-</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>]</mo><mo>&#8746;</mo><mo>[</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo><mo>)</mo></math></p><p>Now,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>&#8746;</mo><mo>[</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&#8734;</mo><mo>)</mo><mo>&#8712;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p>Therefore,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>B</mi><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfenced><mi>c</mi></msup><mo>&#8745;</mo><mi>Z</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"{\" close=\"}\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>5</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p><p>Number of Subsets of above set&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>8</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>256</mn></math></p></blockquote>", "difficulty": "Medium", "source": "JEE Main 2021 (27 Aug Shift 1)", "_marksId": "648b5a6b417cc3fb48d6756d"}]}